        Now I am going to put forth my own thought triggered by this thread.=
 The building up of Chinese(just take Chinese as an example), is accompanied=
 by the process of the=20
development of its culture. In ancient China, approximately the Neolithic a
ge, as held by most scholars, the tribes are ruled by its priests (as also s=
trongly advocated by The Golden Bough, and other dominating schools of the h=
istorians and anthropol
ogists). The writing system are innovated by the priest class to be used to
